Subject: The Hartford- Stock of mp# GTN-0099 Case Number: 11312390
BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.

Goo day, team:

I hope you are doing well. Can you please confirm if the mp# GTN-0099 is still available?

In case the product is EOL, can you please send me a quote for a replacement suggested?

I would appreciate all your support.

Happy New Year!
Bedsaida
CC29
